title: TTC Maya to Aztec - Ancient Mesoamerica Revealed ^ video
description:
TTC Maya to Aztec - Ancient Mesoamerica Revealed ^ Edwin Barnhart ^ compressed video

BOOKLET INCLUDED

This is a compressed copy of another user's upload. The video is shrunk with handbrake and the audio is foobar2000; recombined using MKVToolNix [The quality is very good, all pictures and maps are easy to view]. Included are instructions on how to compress from videos to these tidy MBs. pm me if you want to know how I do it (thanks sup3rman) as it is great for saving space. most ttc content from dohduhdah's uploads at TPB

read the howto text included for what settings were used in compressing these
